name: sato
_description: Do this on a GBKOW RA. Will produce a lvl 99 mag with 5 DEF, 11 POW, 44 DEX, and 39 MIND. Hand it to a VBRW Female FO and feed it 3 more antidote. Will evolve into lvl 100 Sato with stats 5|11|45|39. Total cost is ~103k. Total time is ~11 hrs.
_usage_instructions: rename this file to mags.json and run the .exe in the same directory.
